Package: pigR
Type: Package
Title: Translate English Words and Sentences to Pig Latin
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Johannes", "Breuer", email = "johannes.breuer@gesis.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5906-7873"))
Maintainer: Johannes Breuer <johannes.breuer@gesis.org>
Description: This package provides functions to translate English words and sentences to Pig Latin. It includes two main functions: `pig_word()` for translating individual words and `pig_sentence()` for translating entire sentences. The package follows the rules described in the Pig Latin Wikipedia entry. It handles punctuation, mixed case, and words with no vowels.
